name: Camilla Belle Embedding
description:

Instructions:

Place it in your "embeddings" folder in the Web UI root folder.

Call it out in your prompt with the file name "c4mb3ll".

Weighting for the embed can be adjusted by "(c4mb3ll:1)"

0.95~1 is the recommended weighting.

Your output will vary depending upon your prompt, negative prompt, model, VAE, and Hypernetworks, LORAs etc used.
